      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a dataset where one feature is 'annual income' (ranging from 20k to 500k) and another is 'age' (ranging from 18 to 80). why do i actually need to do feature scaling or normalization before feeding this into a model instead of just leaving it as is?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
